QuestData.Title: WANTED: Rindlewoe
QuestData.Description:
A monstrous beast of wood and flesh has been terrorizing the nearby river territories. Knowing more about how the creature fights may yield interesting data!
Please report any and all findings to Suzie Boltwrench in Krazzlefrazz.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: A monstrous construct, powered by dark magic.
